v 3
d TCA: Transmission Channel Analysis in Dynamic Models
d
d Implements Transmission Channel Analysis (TCA) for structural
d vector autoregressive (SVAR) models following the methodology of
d Wegner, Lieb, and Smeekes (2025) <arXiv:2405.18987>.
d
d TCA decomposes impulse response functions (IRFs) into contributions
d from distinct transmission channels. Supports overlapping channels,
d exhaustive 3-way and 4-way decompositions via inclusion-exclusion.
d
d Requires: Stata 14.0 or later
d
d Author: Muhammad Alkhalaf
d Contact: acad.helper88@gmail.com
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260313
d
f ado/tca.ado
